    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220430/extras/de221f7c78c03b426e6503c50275e2a3.avif?t=1771351046\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experimental nightmare insanity simulator.<br> <br>Point and click.<br>Observe and Contemplate.<br><br>Choose your own path.<br><br>No turning back. No second chances. <br>One chance for each playthrough.<br><br>No hard saving.<br>Completely resets progress when turned off.<br><br>Progress tied to Steam Achievements and the player's curiosity drive to progress.  <br><br>5 Game Modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random Mode: Randomized Permadeath Gameplay Mode<br>Linear Story Mode: Linear order story progression <br>Quick Time Mode: Linear Quick-Time-On-rails Mode with Save State<br>  Marathon Mode: Linear Quick-Time-On-rails Mode with permadeath<br>Puzzle Mode: Search puzzle marathon mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
